        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "srrhP",
          "name": "Spec",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "$color-surface-layer-2",
          "cornerRadius": "$shape-radius-medium-1",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 8,
          "padding": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "cwoFw",
              "name": "Spec Text",
              "fill": "$color-body-default",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "BUTTON — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nShape: pill, cornerRadius = shape-radius-full. Width hugs content; height fixed per size. Line-height 24px across all sizes.\n\nSIZES  (height / font / icon / padding right,left-icon-side / gap)\nSmall     32 / label-small-1 / icon-small-2 / pad-x-small, pad-x-small-3 / gap-x-small\nDefault   40 / label-small-1 / icon-small-2 / pad-x-default, pad-x-small-1 / gap-x-default\nLarge 1   48 / label-default / icon-small-1 / pad-x-large-1, pad-x-default / gap-x-default\nLarge 2   64 / label-large-1 / icon-default / pad-x-large-2, pad-x-large-1 / gap-x-default\nNo Icon = symmetric padding · Icon Only = square, minimal padding.\n\nHIERARCHY (Default polarity)  bg / stroke / text+icon\nPrimary       color-primary / — / color-on-primary\nSecondary     color-secondary / color-line-secondary / color-on-secondary\nTertiary      color-tertiary / — / color-on-tertiary\nDestructive   color-surface-negative / — / color-body-negative\n\nINVERSE polarity  bg / stroke / text+icon\nPrimary       color-primary-inverse / — / color-on-primary-inverse\nSecondary     color-secondary-inverse / color-line-secondary-inverse / color-body-inverse-emphasis\nTertiary      color-tertiary-inverse / — / color-body-inverse-emphasis\nDestructive   color-surface-negative-inverse / — / color-body-inverse-emphasis\n\nSTATES (token suffix on the hierarchy bg) — Primary shown; others follow same -hover/-active/-disabled suffixes\nEnabled color-primary · Hover color-primary-hover · Pressed color-primary-active · Focus color-primary-hover + focus ring · Disabled color-primary-disabled · Busy color-primary-active + inline loader\nFocus ring = OFFSET double ring: inner gap color-surface-base (~4px) then outer ring color-line-focus (~5px).\n   CSS: box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--surface-base), 0 0 0 9px var(--color-line-focus);  (crisp, no blur)\n\nNOTES: width/height/icon-size are literal px (Pencil size props don't bind variables) but equal the named tokens. Icon = lucide 'pencil' placeholder — swap per use. Canvas font Merchant→DM Sans.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$font-family-primary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
