    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "UTSVj",
      "x": 1967.5047690085173,
      "y": 2306,
      "name": "Alert — Component Set",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 804,
      "fill": "$color-surface-base",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": "$gap-content",
      "padding": 48,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "dmUzx",
          "name": "Header",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 6,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "ksyQr",
              "name": "Title",
              "fill": "$color-body-emphasis",
              "content": "Alert",
              "lineHeight": 1.0909,
              "fontFamily": "$font-family-primary",
              "fontSize": "$font-headline-section-size",
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "i0uKDD",
              "name": "Desc",
              "fill": "$color-body-moderate",
              "content": "Communicate conditions, events, and responses to user actions",
              "lineHeight": 1.25,
              "fontFamily": "$font-family-primary",
              "fontSize": "$font-body-supporting-size",
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "wImst",
          "name": "Spec",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "$color-surface-layer-2",
          "cornerRadius": "$shape-radius-medium-1",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 8,
          "padding": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "TUHfl",
              "name": "Spec Text",
              "fill": "$color-body-default",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "ALERT — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nRoot: vertical, width 342 fixed, padding 4/4/4/16 (T R B L), gap 4, radius shape-radius-default, 1px inside border.\nOptical 16px inset = 48px close touch-target + asymmetric padding.\n\nTYPE   bg / border / icon + color\nInfo      surface-info / line-info / info-circle · body-info\nSuccess   surface-positive / line-positive / security-pass · body-positive\nWarning   surface-caution / line-caution / warning-triangle · body-caution\nError     surface-negative-hover / line-negative / warning-circle · body-negative\n\nTitle body-emphasis Body/Default · Supporting body-emphasis Body/Supporting.\nClose 48×48 target + 24 icon, body-emphasis, stroke-default 1.4.  Icon&text gap = gap-x-pair.\nToggles: Show Supporting (off) · Show Close (on) · Show Buttons (off).\nButtons: Action (primary) + Dismiss (tertiary), height-component-small-3, radius-full, Label/Small-1.\nIcons → lucide: info, shield-check, triangle-alert, circle-alert, x (source names info-circle/security-pass/warning-triangle/warning-circle).",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$font-family-primary",
