              "content": "BOTTOM NAV ITEM — SPEC (handoff)\nRoot: vertical, width dimension-56 (568 bp: fill parent), height height-component-default 48 (568: 50), padding 4/0/4/0, gap 0 (568: dimension-2), radius dimension-8, no fill.\nUnselected: outline icon + label (body-moderate), indicator hidden. Selected: filled icon (body-selected) + dot, label hidden.\nPressed (unselected only): icon+label → body-muted. Focus: 2px inside line-focus ring on root.\nIcon = phosphor heart / heart-fill (spec: instance-swap outline/filled pair). Label Label/Small-3.\nNOTE: icon stroke-weight breakpoint diff (small-1 vs default) isn't controllable on Pencil icons; sizes are literal px = tokens.",
