              "name": "Spec Text",
              "fill": "$color-body-default",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "CHECKBOX ITEM — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nRoot: horizontal, height 44px fixed, width hugs content, gap gap-x-component-large.\nAnatomy: Checkbox instance + visible Label. Checkbox retains the two-layer State Layer → Box → Check structure.\nLabel: font-family-primary, Body/Default size + letter spacing, 24px line-height, regular. Default content = Label.\nSelected × State: 2 × 6 = 12 combinations represented by instances of one reusable Checkbox Item source component.\nLabel color: default at rest/error; strong on hover/focus; emphasis on unselected press; muted when disabled.\nFocus: 2px outer line-focus ring. Pressed: 3px outer core-blue-200 ring. Dimensions use literal px where Pencil size properties cannot bind variables reliably.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$font-family-primary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
