              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "DROPDOWN BUTTON — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nRoot: horizontal, 36px high, width hugs content, 8px gap, vertical padding 6px. Anatomy: Label Text + 24px Arrow Icon.\nValue: Closed uses chevron-down; Open uses chevron-up. State: Enabled, Hover, Pressed, Focus, Disabled.\nLabel: DM Sans Label/Large 1, 19px with 24px line-height, regular. Default content = Label.\nFocus: 2px outer color-line-focus ring, 8px radius, 4px horizontal padding. Disabled uses color-body-muted.",
