              "content": "FOOTER — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nViewport variants: Mobile (default, 390px) and Desktop (1440px), represented by instances of one reusable Footer source component.\nOuter padding: 40px vertical / 16px horizontal. Mobile gap 24px; Desktop gap 32px with 32px content-area padding.\nSections: Footer Navigation, Footer Info, and centered Button Container. Navigation has a 1px inverse divider and secondary-inverse CTA.\nScreen Share uses the Primary Inverse Button treatment: white fill with primary-blue label.\nContent properties: Links Heading; Link 1–8; Disclosure 1–8. Links 4–8 default hidden; all disclosures default visible.",
