              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "INLINE TEXT LINK — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nRoot: pure text in a horizontal, center-aligned transparent frame. No icon, loader, or additional wrapper.\nVariants: Default size × 2 emphasis levels × 6 states × 2 polarities = 24 combinations.\nPrimary uses Link/Default typography. Secondary uses Link/Supporting in default polarity and Link/Default in inverse polarity.\nFocus adds 2px horizontal padding, a 2px outer focus ring, and 4px radius. Every example below is an instance of one reusable Inline Text Link source component.",
