              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "LIST ITEM — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nRoot: 358px horizontal row, 16px item gap, center aligned, 16px vertical padding, and 16px radius.\nVariants: 6 types × Tile true/false = 12 combinations. Tile adds surface-base fill and 16px horizontal padding.\nTypes: Navigation, Switch, Details, Details + Nav, Checkbox, and Radio. Optional properties expose the sub-label and 40px leading icon container.\nEvery example below is an instance of one reusable List Item source component.",
