              "content": "LINEAR PROGRESS — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nVariants: Sample Value Low/Medium/High × Size Default/Desktop = 6 combinations.\nDefault is 311 × 130 with a 14px track; Desktop is 560 × 150 with an 18px track.\nThe track uses the blue-to-green score gradient. A 2px vertical indicator marks 400, 625, or 737 within the fixed 400–850 range.\nEvery example below is an instance of one reusable Linear Progress source component.",
