              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "TOGGLE — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nTrack: 52 × 32px, 2px padding, full-radius pill. Handle: 28px circle.\nVariants: Value On/Off × State Enabled/Hover/Focus/Pressed/Disabled = 10 combinations.\nHover uses a 4px blue-100 ring; focus uses a 3px focus ring plus 1px inner line; pressed uses a 4px blue-200 ring.\nShow Icon defaults true and displays the 16px check only when Value=On. Every example below is an instance of one reusable Toggle source.",
