              "id": "x31rYx",
              "name": "Spec Text",
              "fill": "$color-body-default",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "POPOVER TOOLTIP — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nVariants: Show Heading true/false × Position Above/Below/Left/Right × Pointer 25%/Centered/75% = 24 combinations.\nVertical surfaces are 320px wide; horizontal surfaces are 312px wide. Surface padding is 16px with a 12px radius.\nThe 44px close target uses the existing icon system. Pointer and surface use surface-base and elevation-3 shadow tokens.\nEvery example below is an instance of one reusable Popover Tooltip source component.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$font-family-primary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
