              "content": "STATUS TAG — SPEC (design-system handoff)\nVariants: Size Default/Large × Sentiment Informative/Positive/Caution/Negative × Layout No Icon/Left Icon/Right Icon = 24 combinations, plus the reusable master.\nDefault: 28px high, 92px without icon, 112px with icon, 12px icon. Large: 36px high, 100px without icon, 124px with icon, 16px icon.\nAll variants use semantic surface/body tokens, full-radius corners, and Label / Small 1 / Regular. Every example below is an instance of one reusable Status Tag source.",
